#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-28-panache-next-renamed-to-quarkus-data.asciidoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quarkus Hibernate with Panache Next renamed to Quarkus Data Hibernate"
msgstr "Quarkus Hibernate with Panache NextがQuarkus Data Hibernateに名称変更"

#. type: YAML Front Matter: synopsis
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-28-panache-next-renamed-to-quarkus-data.asciidoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "We've renamed Quarkus Hibernate with Panache to Quarkus Data Hibernate, and are looking for feedback"
msgstr "Quarkus Hibernate with PanacheをQuarkus Data Hibernateに改名しました。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-28-panache-next-renamed-to-quarkus-data.asciidoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Goodbye Hibernate with Panache Next… welcome Quarkus Data Hibernate 🥳"
msgstr "さようならHibernate with Panache 次は...ようこそQuarkus Data Hibernate 🥳です。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-05-28-panache-next-renamed-to-quarkus-data.asciidoc
msgid ""
"It's already been a while since we introduced\n"
"link:/blog/hibernate-panache-next[Quarkus Hibernate with Panache Next], and since then, we've decided to\n"
"move closer to the link:https://jakarta.ee/specifications/data/1.1/jakarta-data-1.1-m3[Jakarta Data] standard, as well\n"
"as rename the module to https://quarkus.io/version/main/guides/quarkus-data-hibernate[Quarkus Data Hibernate]."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-28-panache-next-renamed-to-quarkus-data.asciidoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I'll repeat the original disclaimer: this is a new extension, which is experimental, which means everything\n"
"about it can (and probably will) change: the extension name, the package names, the class names\n"
"and even the API. We are releasing it because we feel it's in a good shape to be tested and discussed\n"
"by the community, and we hope to get better feedback before we commit to anything like names or\n"
"API."
msgstr "これは新しい拡張機能であり、実験的なものです。つまり、拡張機能名、パッケージ名、クラス名、そしてAPIまで、すべてが変わる可能性があります(そしておそらく変わるでしょう)。私たちは、コミュニティによってテストされ、議論されるのに適した状態であると感じたので、これをリリースします。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-28-panache-next-renamed-to-quarkus-data.asciidoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Please report feedback either on link:https://quarkusio.zulipchat.com/#narrow/channel/187038-dev/topic/WG.20-.20Quarkus.20Data/with/598039033[Zulip]\n"
"or via link:https://github.com/orgs/quarkusio/projects/50/views/1[GitHub issues]."
msgstr "フィードバックは link:https://quarkusio.zulipchat.com/#narrow/channel/187038-dev/topic/WG.20-.20Quarkus.20Data/with/598039033[Zulip] または link:https://github.com/orgs/quarkusio/projects/50/views/1[GitHub issues] からお願いします。"

